public class GenericDAO<T extends AbstractModel>

      • findByCriteria

        This method is used to get single object or multiple objects based on user criteria.

        Parameters:
        clazz - accepts any model class which extends AbstractModel
        searchCriteria - consists of all restrictions of Criteria
        displayUnique - consists of true or false , if it is true displays a single object else displays multiple objects
        Returns:
        Object if true returns single object else returns multiple objects.
